<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbda129f7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s6371i"><num value="6371i">§ 6371i.</num><heading> Records</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Each recipient of assistance under this part shall keep such records, provide such reports, and furnish such access to books and records as the Secretary may by rule prescribe.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbda129f8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/94/163/tIII/s400">Pub. L. 94–163, title III, § 400</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/95/619/tIII/s302/a">Pub. L. 95–619, title III, § 302(a)</ref>, <date date="1978-11-09">Nov. 9, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/3247">92 Stat. 3247</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/105/388/s5/a/11">Pub. L. 105–388, § 5(a)(11)</ref>, <date date="1998-11-13">Nov. 13, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/3479">112 Stat. 3479</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
