<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idbda129fb-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1998—<ref href="/us/pl/105/388">Pub. L. 105–388</ref> struck out “(a)” before “Each recipient”.</p>
